    "akari_span_text_18": "Song/impersonation",
    "akari_span_text_19": "🎤 Overwhelming singing ability",
    "akari_span_text_20": "She has a reputation for her singing ability among Aogiri High School students, and the video of her singing ``Romeo and Cinderella'' has achieved over a million views. During the Stogura project, she performed ``Marunouchi Sadistic'' a cappella and received great praise from her co-stars.",
    "akari_span_text_21": "🎭 Exquisite impersonation",
    "akari_span_text_22": "She says that she doesn't have the aptitude for voice imitation, and when she imitates Hamtaro and Togepi, she often creates an exquisite atmosphere (that's also her charm!).",
    "akari_span_text_23": "in-game legend",
    "akari_span_text_24": "🔫 Red Gang \"Santa Claus\" Boss",
    "akari_strong_text_7": "From beginner to boss:",
    "akari_span_text_25": "Although she is a beginner who doesn't know right from left, she starts her own gang and becomes the (temporary) boss. The theme color is red, and the fruit motif is dragon fruit.",
    "akari_strong_text_8": "Beloved boss:",
    "akari_span_text_26": "There were times when I cried at the end of the stream due to pressure, but I was supported by early members such as Mukuro, Woo-chan, Yona, and Kon, as well as strong experienced members such as Amuro, Light, Mondo, and Vanilla.",
    "akari_strong_text_9": "Conquer all major crimes:",
    "akari_span_text_27": "She grew through the bonds with her friends, and eventually accomplished the great feat of conquering all major crimes!",
    "akari_span_text_28": "⛏️ Architecture and sense of direction",
    "akari_strong_text_10": "Lost child skills:",
    "akari_span_text_29": "She worries about building the roof of her home and goes on a journey to find materials, but due to her extreme lack of direction, she sometimes loses track of the home she built.",
    "akari_strong_text_11": "Underground torture chamber:",
    "akari_span_text_30": "When collaborating with Rie Gabe and Reiko Oto, she intended to make the basement of her home more stylish, but for some reason it ended up looking like a \"prison (torture chamber)\" with iron bars and a toilet.",
    "akari_strong_text_12": "Efforts behind the scenes:",
    "akari_span_text_31": "Even outside of streaming, she is so obsessed with Minecraft that she builds infinite generation facilities and immerses herself in collecting materials.",
    "chiyomi_link_text": "← Return to member list",
    "chiyomi_span_40kg": "Idol with a grip strength of 40kg",
    "chiyomi_span_text": "Chomi Chiyoura",
    "chiyomi_span_text_2": "\"I'm going to crush everyone's hearts at Aogiri High School!\"",
    "chiyomi_span_text_3": "butterfly",
