    "chiyomi_span_text_7": "Basic profile",
    "chiyomi_strong_text": "Affiliation/Grade:",
    "chiyomi_span_1": "Aogiri High School 1st year student",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_2": "Birthday/Age:",
    "chiyomi_span_25_22": "February 5th / Eternal 22 years old (Fairy)",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_3": "Height/grip strength:",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_4": "Special skill:",
    "chiyomi_span_text_8": "piano, perfect pitch",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_5": "Previous job (previous life):",
    "chiyomi_span_text_9": "Former announcer. When she wakes up one day, she finds herself in the body of a high school girl and decides to become an idol!",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_6": "Dreams/goals:",
    "chiyomi_span_text_10": "Holding solo live performances and singing theme songs for anime and games.",
    "chiyomi_span_text_11": "Delivery characteristics",
    "chiyomi_span_text_12": "Nostalgic song frame (Roboson specialized)",
    "chiyomi_span_90200050": "Mainly anime songs from the 90's to 2000's. She is particularly good at robot anime songs (Robothong) such as Gundam, and can sing over 50 Gundam theme songs alone.",
    "chiyomi_span_text_13": "Challenging live-action streaming",
    "chiyomi_span_text_14": "Although she is an idol, she puts her body on the line by cooking and eating ``insect foods'' such as tarantulas, scorpions, and giant tortoises, as well as ``game food'' such as crows and geckos.",
    "chiyomi_span_text_15": "creativity",
    "chiyomi_span_dtm": "She studied songwriting and composition (DTM) on her own and produced and performed original songs such as ``Moon to Taiyo'' and ``Yumeoi no Chou.''",
    "chiyomi_span_text_16": "Various fan names (faction)",
    "chiyomi_span_text_17": "All fan names are",
    "chiyomi_strong_text_7": "\"Chiyomin\"",
    "chiyomi_span_text_18": "However, there are separate factions based on the tone of Chiyo-chan's voice that appears in the stream.",
    "chiyomi_span_text_19": "Loli Chiyo",
    "chiyomi_span_text_20": "Newly",
    "chiyomi_span_text_21": "Sister",
    "chiyomi_span_text_22": "Little brother",
    "chiyomi_span_text_23": "Tsunchiyo",
    "chiyomi_span_text_24": "childhood friend",
    "chiyomi_span_text_25": "Yang Chiyo",
    "chiyomi_span_text_26": "darling",
    "chiyomi_span_text_27": "Chiyobaba",
    "chiyomi_span_text_28": "grandchild",
    "chiyomi_span_text_29": "*Other derivatives such as “Gal Chiyo” and “Shota Chiyo” also exist!",
    "chiyomi_span_text_30": "List of terms and quotes",
    "chiyomi_span_text_31": "From dream to reality (episode)",
    "chiyomi_span_text_32": "🦴 Even if you break a bone, it doesn't happen for free.",
    "chiyomi_span_text_33": "Although she has sprained (or fractured) her chest bone in the past, she has a strong heart (and grip strength) that allows her to sublimate it into stories such as ``Broken Bullet Travel.''",
    "chiyomi_span_text_34": "📻 Dream come true (radio and live)",
    "chiyomi_span_2days": "Fans are captivated by the way she continues to fulfill her dreams one after another, such as becoming a solo radio personality on Nippon Cultural Broadcasting and holding her long-awaited first solo live (2 days) at Kanda Myojin Hall.",
    "etra_link_text": "← Return to member list",
    "etra_span_text": "Etra",
    "etra_span_text_2": "“Being able to dilute more accurately than anyone else”",
    "etra_span_text_3": "#voice big science",
    "etra_span_text_4": "#extreme rain girl",
    "etra_span_text_5": "#Focusing on the buttocks",
    "etra_span_text_6": "#Equipment serious",
    "etra_span_text_7": "Basic profile",
    "etra_strong_text": "Debut date:",
    "etra_span_201992": "September 2, 2019",
    "etra_strong_text_2": "birthday:",
    "etra_span_721": "July 21st (a date I decided with listeners on a farm game stream a long time ago)",
    "etra_strong_text_3": "Age/Height:",
    "etra_span_17_170cm175cm": "Self-proclaimed 17 years old / over 170cm (height is about 175cm including heels)",
    "etra_strong_text_4": "Origin of business card badge (umbrella):",
    "etra_span_5": "Because she is an extreme ``rain woman'' (there is a legend that all the marathons she ran during her student days were canceled for five years due to rain or snow).",
    "etra_strong_text_5": "Audience gender ratio:",
    "etra_span_25975": "The overwhelming majority of listeners are male, with 2.5% female and 97.5% male.",
    "etra_span_text_8": "Hobbies/preferences",
    "etra_span_text_9": "🍴 Favorite food/alcohol",
    "etra_span_text_10": "Peach, Chinese food, Morning Mac Egg McMuffin. High on plum wine and apple cider vinegar.",
    "etra_span_text_11": "🎨 Favorite color/scent",
    "etra_span_text_12": "Navy blue (most of my clothes are white). Lavender scent.",
    "etra_span_text_13": "🐕 Favorite animal/Pokémon",
    "etra_span_text_14": "Mokurow, Lucario, Absol. I love both dogs and cats, but unfortunately I'm allergic to both.",
    "etra_span_text_15": "😢 Works that made me cry",
    "etra_span_10": "Movie “Pokémon Lucario the Movie”, book “10 Promises between My Dog and Me”",
    "etra_span_text_16": "Special skills & ❌ Things I’m not good at",
    "etra_strong_text_6": "✅ Accurate dilution:",
    "etra_span_text_17": "With a science background (inorganic chemistry in the biological field), she boasts of being able to dilute things more accurately than anyone else.",
    "etra_strong_text_7": "✅ Specialty dishes:",
    "etra_span_text_18": "Roast beef (because it can be made in a rice cooker).",
    "etra_strong_text_8": "❌ General weaknesses:",
    "etra_span_text_19": "Memorization, drawing, public speaking, continuing (extreme boredom).",
    "etra_strong_text_9": "❌ Sense of direction:",
    "etra_span_text_20": "I'm not good at understanding the positional relationships and three-dimensional structures of things, so I often get lost.",
    "etra_strong_text_10": "❌ Lack of sleep:",
    "etra_span_text_21": "Absolute enemy (because it makes you sick).",
    "etra_span_text_22": "Distribution/equipment environment (serious)",
    "etra_strong_text_11": "keyboard:",
    "etra_span_niz": "I love the NiZ capacitive contactless keyboard (English layout).",
    "etra_strong_text_12": "microphone:",
    "etra_strong_if": "Audio IF:",
    "etra_span_ur22cyamaha": "UR22C (YAMAHA)",
    "etra_strong_daw": "DAW software:",
    "etra_span_text_23": "Legend of Etra (interesting episode)",
    "etra_span_text_24": "Laughter is too loud",
    "etra_span_text_25": "Once, the laughter and responses were so loud that they penetrated the studio door and echoed all the way to the elevator hall.",
    "etra_span_text_26": "Commitment to the buttocks",
    "etra_span_text_27": "The company has a good reputation for its butts, with sales of ``butt mouse pads'' and ``scale figures made from butts.'' When making the figure, she requested, ``I want you to create an angle that won't be embarrassing for fans when they buy it.''",
    "etra_span_text_28": "Broadcasting accident (?)",
    "etra_span_v": "When she appeared on ``Galibenger V'' in the early days of her career, there was an incident where the accuracy of the glove-shaped tracker was poor, and when she was resting her hands on her lap, only her middle finger stood up, which caused her to panic.",
    "garu_link_text": "← Return to member list",
